  "body": "- [ ] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nIt looks like the truffle does not produce apple arm artifacts when compiling on apple m1\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n`npm install -ddd --global --build-from-source --cache=/Users/rchen/Library/Caches/Homebrew/npm_cache --prefix=/usr/local/Cellar/truffle/5.4.6/libexec /path/to/truffle-5.4.6.tgz`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nTo see the apple arm64 artifacts got built\r\n\r\nRight now this is what I can see on apple m1 environment (but not seeing it in x86_64 arch)\r\n```\r\n  * Binaries built for a non-native architecture were installed into truffle's prefix.\r\n    The offending files are:\r\n      /opt/homebrew/Cellar/truffle/5.4.3/libexec/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/bufferutil/prebuilds/darwin-x64/node.napi.node\t(x86_64)\r\n      /opt/homebrew/Cellar/truffle/5.4.3/libexec/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/fsevents/fsevents.node\t(x86_64)\r\n      /opt/homebrew/Cellar/truffle/5.4.3/libexec/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/keccak/prebuilds/darwin-x64/node.napi.node\t(x86_64)\r\n      /opt/homebrew/Cellar/truffle/5.4.3/libexec/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/leveldown/prebuilds/darwin-x64/node-napi.node\t(x86_64)\r\n      /opt/homebrew/Cellar/truffle/5.4.3/libexec/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/secp256k1/prebuilds/darwin-x64/node.napi.node\t(x86_64)\r\n      /opt/homebrew/Cellar/truffle/5.4.3/libexec/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/utf-8-validate/prebuilds/darwin-x64/node.napi.node\t(x86_64)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nThe audit failure above.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: macOS 11.0-arm (apple m1)\r\n* Ethereum client:\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.4.6\r\n* node version (`node --version`): 16.6.2\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 7.20.3\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nrelates to https://github.com/Homebrew/homebrew-core/pull/82278",
